the SEDTC is added to wqm_con.npt for sediment temperature calculation 

SED_TEMP in makefile is for sed temperature calculation

WET_DRY in makefile for wetting and drying with casename_run.dat to turn it on or off

HYDRO_INTERP is option for interpolating hydrodynamics

DTI is not anymore read from wqm_con.npt, it is given the same as DLT 

